{"tid":1763392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】港人冰室起義資源分享 上限每周$700 助抗爭年輕人解困","createTime":"2019-11-30T09:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T04:10:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"38df9197770e1949078ea04691363207dc42cd3a","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"年輕人勇於站在抗爭最前線，觸動不少成年人，有和理非變勇武聲援，又有人自發組家長車管接管送各司其職，新近就有名為「香港人冰室資源分享」的組織成立，由有心人注資，租下工廈單位，審批要「快狠準」，儼如民間社署，向因抗爭而面對經濟困難的年輕人提供現金券及定額八達通，每星期以700元為上限，暫解食和行的燃眉之急。據了解，參與成立工作室的，既有前線社工，也有為抗爭者提供免費法律支援的律師及商人，落實以社區資源共享方式，在非常時期，與年輕人共渡難關。<br />\n<br />\n香港人冰室資源分享社交媒體專頁周一（25/11）正式運作，以一幅寫着「光復香港 時代革命」的插畫為專頁標記，報稱慈善性質，開宗明義「希望守護香港年輕人」，讓小孩子溫飽，甚至願意長期承擔醫藥費，承諾「面對亂世選擇用良心做決策」等。同為「冰室」，業務大不同，自反修例風波以來，一直瞓身支持年輕人的龍門冰室老闆張俊傑，在接受《蘋果》查詢時，就笑說兩間冰室雖然都以香港人優先，但並無直接關係。<br />\n<br />\n而對於是否「幕後金主」，張俊傑沒否認也沒承認，只說今日香港，「每個真香港人都希望出一分力」，他表示過去不少有心人到小店吃飯，結賬時往往放低多於飯錢的鈔票，叮囑代請年輕人食飯，由於數量不少，故已下令員工不能代收，但今後會在5間分店的收銀機旁放置「心意箱」，權充中介平台，並承諾會將箱內心意直接轉「香港人冰室資源分享」，轉交有需要的年輕人。此外，由於近日天氣轉冷，他表示龍門冰室位於紅磡的分店，亦會代收適合年輕人的二手外套，轉交有需要的年輕人手上。<br />\n<br />\n如此，大抵有搞革命的氣概了。百多年前，香港商人捨命投入家產，始有後來的起義；如今，各路人馬組成的工作室，其實在部份非公開的家長谷早廣泛流傳，任何25歲以下年輕人或被捕人士，經由社工在內的團隊通過簡單審批程序，包括提供年齡、姓名和基本背景資料，可獲批每星期550元現金券和150元面額的八達通等，不會有現金交收，避免承擔不必要的法律風險。本身是律師的Hermes，是工作室的義務法律顧問，他表示早前因協助一名被捕年輕人而認識發起人，認同工作室理念，所以加入成為一分子。<br />\n<br />\n據知，工作室已獲有心人首階段注資30萬元作起動資金，目標是支持抗爭者基本生活，與現時612基金和星火等主要提供法律支援沒重叠。除現金券，月中已在九龍東租用一單位，備梳化床和浴室，以供抗爭者有需要時可休息及淋浴。不願透露身份的其中一名成員謂，眼見不少年輕人因政見不同而與家人鬧翻，遭經濟封鎖無家可歸，希望藉實際支持，讓年輕人感受到社會關心，更希望吸引更多同路人與年輕人繼續同行。<br />\n<br />\n「宗旨其實係網頁上面咁寫：希望下一個幫助人的是你，呢啲年輕人，今日受過別人恩惠，他朝搵到錢要幫有需要嘅人，就係咁簡單。」成員都說，抗爭道路漫長，隨時是數月甚至數年，就算最終林鄭下台，亦不代表運動告一段落。事實上，歷時近半年的反修例運動，就是在區選泛民大勝後，如何繼續走下去，也是必須反思的難題。由街頭回歸選舉、發展黃色經濟圈等，也是選項。與家人鬧翻的文仔，因一場逆權運動而淪為雙失，現僅靠疼錫他的阿姨接濟生活，對於新成立的工作室，他直言在圈子內有所聞，最初亦擔心工作室是「陷阱」，後透過不同途徑確認搞手身份，較為安心，有需要時亦會去申請。<br />\n<br />\n一直支持抗爭年輕人的龍門冰室老闆張俊傑，直言運動發展到今日，一直思考可做到甚麼。「一開始推出免費學生餐，就係睇到好多學生同年輕人，因為同屋企人政見不同，被經濟封鎖唔畀零用錢、又唔畀佢返去屋企，搞到無錢食飯無地方瞓，希望可以幫到佢哋，再慢慢演變落去，就喺幾間餐廳門口擺啲嘢食嘢飲、提供唔同嘅資源，但係慢慢就聽到好多人留言，話有啲年輕人真係有需要你幫，但因為唔好意思，所以唔嚟食呢個免費餐；而擺喺門口嘅嘢食嘢飲，亦都係畀一啲無需要嘅人攞咗去，甚至變賣變成錢，失去原來嘅意義。」<br />\n<br />\n張俊傑直言認同「資源分享」的原則，強調「只要係幫到年輕人嘅事，我一定支持」，「過去好多客人嚟我哋舖頭食嘢，成日係食50蚊但畀100蚊就走咗去，我哋夥計追出去，就同我哋講，話想出少少力，幫吓啲小朋友。既然係咁，我不如乾脆放個箱喺度，大家嚟食嘢就好，想幫小朋友嘅錢或者現金券，就放喺呢個箱度，我哋會直接交去工作室。」張謂提供學生餐始終較被動，遇到就幫，遇不到就只能自生自滅，認為一個公開的平台，有實際需要。<br />\n<br />\n「612同星火，其實都做緊法律援助嘅工作，但審批相對繁複，可能因為被捕嘅人實在太多，有啲需要真係未必照顧到，我親身嘅經歷係，上次紅磡拉咗70個細路，而星火就只可派兩位律師落去幫佢哋做擔保，好明顯資源亦不足，後來輾轉我先搵咗位律師朋友，幫我夥計個女搞踢保。」面對亂局，他認為不同人可各司其職，除了法律援助，香港人最基本就是衣食住行：「我有個理想，希望可以資源分享，由有心人擺一筆錢落去，做基本營運資金，而我亦會諗辦法每日貢獻部份錢落去，等佢可以繼續運作，幫到有需要嘅人。」<br />\n<br />\n張說心目中的資源分享工作間，會有一幅連儂牆，受惠的年輕人可以協助裝飾和幫手設計文宣、管理網站，甚至協助宣傳公民意識，用工作換取報酬。「我接觸嘅年輕人，大部份都好有骨氣，唔好意思白白攞資助&hellip;&hellip;可能一開始資源分享嘅資金唔大，咁咪睇餸食飯，先集中喺食同行方面，提供各樣嘅飯券又或者一啲交通資助，等佢哋可以保持到正常日常嘅生活，第日當然希望發展落去，可以做到真係照顧到衣食住行各方面。」<br />\n<br />\n除了現金券，他說亦想製造就業機會：「因為今次運動，好多人被捕停學或失去職業，原本可以做醫生、律師；有消防員因為咁無咗份工，如工作室可提供受薪職位，甚至成為受薪董事，負責審批的工作，就可運用資金去幫有需要嘅年輕人，佢哋感同身受，更加知道邊啲人應該幫&hellip;&hellip;其實大學讀嗰樣，到出嚟做嘢，未必真係要做嗰科嘅工作。」就如他，大學讀精算，卻跑了去搞茶餐廳，他笑說條條大路通羅馬，只在乎跌倒時是否有人願意扶一把。<br />\n<br />\n「今日可能你需要人哋幫你，但到將來你搵到錢，就到你幫番有需要的人，呢樣嘢其實喺香港係失傳咗好耐，我以前屋企好窮，無得食都係隔籬屋鄰居煮埋，然後叫你去食，無佢哋幫忙可能都無今日嘅我。」物換星移，一場運動，香港面目全非，藍黃大戰、警民關係惡劣，但有失也有得，就如這種守望相助的人情味，阿傑說以為早已失傳，但在今日已無法回頭的香港，他期望否極泰來，可在社區再現。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191128/large/1574928924_ee6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191128%2Flarge%2F1574928924_ee6a.png&h=635b758f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191128/large/1574924535_ea55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191128%2Flarge%2F1574924535_ea55.jpg&h=5d825ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191130/60319476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60319476&d=ZahK9au6JYDyKCuDEpipf%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=09c946d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191130%2F60319476&h=d922303d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191130/60319476</a>"},{"pid":"a4c616a4e6a1b87fa5c9e48fdf82a18866815f8d","tid":1763392,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d32dae69b0c2d63eb3dd3b621b1000d8fe3a5f5","tid":1763392,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"點課金？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62367678092cc21bddb79db5682cb5e13ca47767","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d32dae69b0c2d63eb3dd3b621b1000d8fe3a5f5","tid":1763392,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"點課金？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zh2GuSB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZh2GuSB.jpg&h=c314fee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我諗你要自己用TG嚟同佢哋溝通啦"},{"pid":"f79e97dc6843a9a12027c10c02f586c750af72e1","tid":1763392,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe12626d3890104f1fe50e3f4ee3c35fabfe1d","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"22f363daac5bad34fdaa6a71bdbf17e189ba972b","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:11:45.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"d4e968906799e97d54bf1ee624c8bfad19d4b87f","tid":1763392,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ec1347f134d42791949c50cefb1ce50a618fbc","tid":1763392,"uid":238451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c8b66c84e2fd979fdefd96a75f322a181e621321","tid":1763392,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:20:25.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"723e434b93cc355d4865bd3f6117c2985d5eba1d","tid":1763392,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"即係出錢助養山區兒童就搵佢？"},{"pid":"468906e647928d503b12af1f9e928e84fe411aed","tid":1763392,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:26:36.000Z","msg":"nice"},{"pid":"2dcb9a979752ede827b8181bb4671ce19f93fd9f","tid":1763392,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:33:57.000Z","msg":"點解政府同藍絲到依家都未清醒?<br />\n就算手足玩雞尾酒，養鶳，<br />\n但都仍然有海嘯咁勁嘅民意，<br />\n連區議會都可以玩到班保皇爛閪，<br />\n再加上依家黃色經濟圈，<br />\n真係遲早架空成個政府唔係夢..."},{"pid":"a661447c8a522b204e0b9bd98fda5b6cae3dcdb4","tid":1763392,"uid":180561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9383f8d84979147657c598d5864059607d6ad01f","tid":1763392,"uid":254976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a1f4a7ca225d894085ab7722f8d03e9447bd0f97","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"723e434b93cc355d4865bd3f6117c2985d5eba1d","tid":1763392,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"即係出錢助養山區兒童就搵佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以試吓，至少多個途徑幫手"},{"pid":"aecfe8b26d8beb3b6cc0d173b4f97ffc0bbcb0e8","tid":1763392,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:50:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e74dad2d245180dd2378da793a5a237ce8904a2","tid":1763392,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b22b08ee90509aca6898e866546ac9bbe4798f","tid":1763392,"uid":57815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T06:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82dea3be88731b046e658904a350edf60a6facc","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e74dad2d245180dd2378da793a5a237ce8904a2","tid":1763392,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T05:30:46.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1337586eae75d56207d89f1fef85aacce4a61c17","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:26:35.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"d553343ecc598895f12f03b3697e5cae456bdaf1","tid":1763392,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:32:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dad8fb05c4b3a96211dfba667e489eeebd51c5fd","tid":1763392,"uid":283173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:37:02.000Z","msg":"每個餐室收銀前有個細箱(冇寫捐款箱，要問收銀姐姐)入落去就得，食完早餐順手入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063ea7a7ee85819a3deac9c90df99c7b23c9d7b0","tid":1763392,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dad8fb05c4b3a96211dfba667e489eeebd51c5fd","tid":1763392,"uid":283173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T23:37:02.000Z","msg":"每個餐室收銀前有個細箱(冇寫捐款箱，要問收銀姐姐)入落去就得，食完早餐順手入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:29:23.000Z","msg":"Thx for sharing"},{"pid":"b993cedb3ef1f2a077eb1bcf801f8b38e24f086c","tid":1763392,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"呢個一定要推，重要過法律援助"}]}